data.value: Dim bmp As New Bitmap(PictureBox25.Image) Dim bmp2 As New Bitmap(bmp.Width, bmp.Height) Dim r, g, b As Int32 For x = 1 To bmp.Width - 1 For y = 1 To bmp.Height - 1 x1 = bmp.GetPixel(x, y) x2 = bmp2.GetPixel(x, y) r = x1.R g = x1.G b = x1.B 'bmp2.SetPixel(x, y, Color.FromArgb(0, g, 0)) If x - bmp.Width / 50 < 0 Then Else bmp2.SetPixel(x - bmp.Width / 50, y, Color.FromArgb(x2.R, x2.G, b)) End If If x + bmp.Width / 50 > bmp.Width Then Else bmp2.SetPixel(x + bmp.Width / 50 - 1, y, Color.FromArgb(r, x2.G, x2.B)) End If PictureBox24.BackgroundImage = bmp2 Next Next
